title: Up and Running with GoToMeeting with David Rivers
description:
Lynda.com - Up and Running with GoToMeeting
1h 42m Appropriate for all Jan 15, 2014


You can easily work face-to-face with anyone anywhere with GoToMeeting, so get up and running and start collaborating now. In this course, David Rivers teaches you everything from how to set up GoToMeeting, manage groups, and organize meetings to the basics of attending a meeting via email, website, or device. Topics include:

    Installing GoToMeeting
    Integrating GoToMeeting with Office, Outlook, and Lync
    Scheduling meetings
    Inviting attendees
    Starting and ending meetings
